[22/12/2017 14:29:03] <font color="#ffffff">¿De qué tipo?</font>
[22/12/2017 14:29:05] <font color="#ffffff">Tomme de Saboya.</font>
[22/12/2017 14:29:05] <font color="#ffffff">Tomme de Saboya.</font>
[22/12/2017 14:29:08] <font color="#ffffff">Con leche de cabra o de vaca.</font>
[22/12/2017 14:29:10] <font color="#ffffff">No he probado</font>
